{"tid":778854,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★少年股神大對決！看好科技板塊，尤其是騰訊、瑞聲科技和舜宇光學","createTime":"2018-08-14T04:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T04:55:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ee8a9cf0a212d7301ec39f69f8acb81d4c0822dd","tid":778854,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:08:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>科技板塊絕對看好</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他續指，年內恒指累升逾23%，就算單月內下跌2,000點亦不意外。<br />\n<br />\n他最看好科技板塊，尤其是騰訊、瑞聲科技(02018)和舜宇光學科技(02382)。他指，科技股增長動力強，且未來改變大眾生活毋庸置疑，故絕對看好。惟他提醒，一定要揀行業領頭羊。但騰訊本周三公布業績，不妨績後再作打算。<br />\n<br />\n他也看好滙豐控股(00005)，指該股業績表現理想兼有回購支持，有望升上80元水平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/finance/20170815/00269_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170815%2F00269_001.html&d=8wRfes4BNiqzHQc1cLrktv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=934584fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/finance/20170815/00269_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a4d44f76de5e9941e54f41ee885bfed099d501e2","tid":778854,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfee54fbce13aa9d1922fa7c37433ba995551ce","tid":778854,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/finance/20170815/photo/0815-00269-001b2.jpg?t=1534219745635\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170815%2Fphoto%2F0815-00269-001b2.jpg%3Ft%3D1534219745635&h=ec4c7df0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e30c9254445ac83c4d91552142c1039db8f55a5","tid